(6035, 1, '2017-09-29 15:39:38', '2017-09-29 13:39:38', 'John has been working in commercial video and digital production for over 10 years. He likes working with super talented people to create dope visuals and interactive experiences.\n\nOriginally an offline editor in short-form commercial video, he has strong technical chops that make him a hands-on producer today. He\'s worked with a wide range of production companies, vfx and design studios and advertising agencies on everything from broadcast tv spots, websites, integrated media campaigns to music videos, short films, interactive installations, and other multimedia bric-a-brac.\n\nAlumnus of award winning design and production studio <a href="http://weareroyale.com">We Are Royale</a>. Recently producer at creative advertising agency <a href="http://www.achtung.nl">Achtung! mcgarrybowen Amsterdam</a> & <a href="http://studiokraftwerk.com">Studio Kraftwerk</a>.\n\nHe is based out of Amsterdam where he\'s freelancing and working on his Nederlands taalvaardigheid. For current availability <a href="#contact">drop him a line</a>. ', 'John Gerard', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4963-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-09-29 15:39:38', '2017-09-29 13:39:38', '', 4963, 'http://localhost/4963-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
